-你喜欢敞篷车，是吗？-是的
-You like a convertible, don't you? -Yeah.

1064
01:02:03,760 --> 01:02:06,839
那为什么我们不用敞篷车来跑一场拉力赛呢？
Why don't we rally-drive convertibles?

1065
01:02:07,000 --> 01:02:09,279
-那会很脏。-现在，请跟着我做一件事
-It's too dusty. -Now, do one thing for me,

1066
01:02:09,360 --> 01:02:11,079
我们去找些敞篷车
we're going to go and get some convertibles,

1067
01:02:11,760 --> 01:02:13,599
然后把它们改装成拉力赛车跑拉力赛！
turn them into rally cars and do that!

1068
01:02:14,040 --> 01:02:15,479
我不会跑拉力赛
I can't do rally driving.

1069
01:02:15,760 --> 01:02:17,639
-这很简单，只要...-我不行！
-It's easy, just... -I can't!

1070
01:02:17,720 --> 01:02:19,079
我不能在野地里开车...
I can't drive on loose surfaces...

1071
01:02:23,680 --> 01:02:25,519
这就是我的座驾
This is what I've got.

1072
01:02:25,600 --> 01:02:27,839
日产350Z
Nissan 350Z.

1073
01:02:30,320 --> 01:02:31,599
3.5升V6引擎
Three-and-a-half-litre V6,

1074
01:02:31,680 --> 01:02:34,759
276制动马力，后驱
276 brake horsepower, rear-wheel drive.

1075
01:02:36,840 --> 01:02:38,599
现在，你看着这车，可能在想“好吧
Now, you might be looking at it, thinking, "Well,

1076
01:02:39,200 --> 01:02:40,879
这车看上去不怎么像拉力赛车”
"it doesn't look much like a rally car."

1077
01:02:41,280 --> 01:02:43,999
但先别急着下定论，这车有一个血亲
But hold on,this car is a direct descendant

1078
01:02:44,080 --> 01:02:45,719
日产Datsun 240Z
of the Datsun 240Z,

1079
01:02:45,800 --> 01:02:48,439
一款曾经横扫世界拉力锦标赛的名车
a car that owned world rallying.

1080
01:02:48,520 --> 01:02:50,879
所以它有拉力血统
So this has got history.

1081
01:02:51,520 --> 01:02:52,959
它会表现很出色
It's going to be brilliant.

1082
01:02:59,840 --> 01:03:00,879
我找到一辆宝马
I've got a BMW.

1083
01:03:02,040 --> 01:03:05,079
没有拉力血统，我选它因为我喜欢这车
No history of rallying at all,it's one of the reasons I like it.

1084
01:03:05,080 --> 01:03:07,079
好吧，说说看，给观众介绍介绍这车的引擎？
Well, come on, tell us about it,what engine has it got?

1085
01:03:07,080 --> 01:03:08,679
2.5升直列6缸
Two-and-a-half-litre straight 6.

1086
01:03:08,760 --> 01:03:10,919
哈蒙德：排量比日产低了1000cc。动力呢？
HAMMOND: 1000cc less than the Nissan. Power?

1087
01:03:11,600 --> 01:03:13,279
我猜大概192？
192?

1088
01:03:13,520 --> 01:03:15,519
那也比我的车少了80马力。扭矩多大？
That's about 80 horsepower less.Torque?

1089
01:03:16,080 --> 01:03:17,079
180牛米
180.

1090
01:03:17,160 --> 01:03:19,479
-同样低了80。-很好！
-That's about 80 torques less. -Good!

1091
01:03:19,560 --> 01:03:20,879
-你说很好啥意思？-很好！
-What do you mean, "good"? -Good!

1092
01:03:20,960 --> 01:03:23,999
杰瑞米，你没有表现出真正的竞赛精神
Jeremy, you're not really getting into the competitive spirit of this.

1093
01:03:24,080 --> 01:03:27,039
我不喜欢在没有附着力的地面上开车！
I don't like driving without friction!

1094
01:03:27,400 --> 01:03:29,559
哈蒙德：敞篷拉力赛将会是下一个兴起的运动大项
HAMMOND: Open-top rally is going to be the next big thing.

1095
01:03:29,640 --> 01:03:32,079
让我们开始改装我们的战车吧
Let's go and convert these into rally cars.

1096
01:03:33,560 --> 01:03:37,079
接下来是激情改装加配乐时间
This meant finding a workshop and cueing the music.

1097
01:03:38,000 --> 01:03:38,999
（过场音乐）
(THEA-TEAMTHEME PLAYING)

1098
01:03:42,760 --> 01:03:43,759
克拉克森：搞定
CLARKSON: Got it.

1099
01:03:48,520 --> 01:03:49,519
噢，很好
Oh, yes.

1100
01:03:49,680 --> 01:03:50,679
老天，我真天才
God, I'm good.

1101
01:03:53,360 --> 01:03:56,279
这会让我的战车小宇宙爆发
That will make up for the horsepower deficit

1102
01:03:56,360 --> 01:03:57,799
哈蒙德的车上也有这个
that I have on Richard's car.

1103
01:04:01,120 --> 01:04:02,879
我是八月车神
This is August.

1104
01:04:06,640 --> 01:04:08,039
请叫我四月骑士
Now Mr April.

1105
01:04:17,040 --> 01:04:19,399
我的防滚架完工
My roll-cage is complete.

1106
01:04:27,440 --> 01:04:30,039
哈蒙德：第二天，我们的车都已蓄势待发
HAMMOND: The next day,our cars were ready.

1107
01:04:30,280 --> 01:04:33,479
-老天爷也很给面子。-（电闪雷鸣）
-And so was the sky. -(THUNDER CRACKING)

1108
01:04:40,280 --> 01:04:42,199
万事俱备，只欠东风
This is alljust fantastic.

1109
01:04:42,280 --> 01:04:44,719
突然间，完美的拉力天气也即将降临
Suddenly, perfect rallying weather is coming.

1110
01:04:45,160 --> 01:04:47,759
一点点雨水，泥土，山间的薄雾
Bit of rain, mud, mist on the hills,

1111
01:04:47,840 --> 01:04:50,079
我的车已经准备就绪
and my car is now perfect.

1112
01:04:50,240 --> 01:04:52,239
并没有爆改
Haven't gone over the top with the modifications.

1113
01:04:52,440 --> 01:04:54,639
只是换了新轮毂，新轮胎，加装了防滚架
New wheels, new tyres, roll-cage,

1114
01:04:54,960 --> 01:04:56,999
赞助商贴纸，不能用真的
sponsorship stickers,can't have real ones,

1115
01:04:57,080 --> 01:04:59,639
这是BBC的规定，但我们尽可能营造真实气氛
BBC objects, but we've made 'em up to put you in the mood.

1116
01:04:59,840 --> 01:05:03,719
内部，拉力座椅，多点式安全带，足够了
Inside, racing seat,full harness, that's enough.

1117
01:05:04,120 --> 01:05:05,639
这会是一次另人惊叹的比赛
This is going to be amazing.

1118
01:05:08,360 --> 01:05:09,359
我就是学着他的样子依葫芦画瓢而已
I just copied him.

1119
01:05:10,520 --> 01:05:14,159
现在他准备开着他的日产在泥地里撒欢了
And now he's going to drive about in his Datsun in the mud.

1120
01:05:18,080 --> 01:05:20,719
哈蒙德：他说的没错，我已经迫不及待了
HAMMOND: He was right, I couldn't wait.

1121
01:05:27,600 --> 01:05:29,079
噢，真爽！
Oh, yes!

1122
01:05:30,400 --> 01:05:33,199
真的下雨了，我在跑拉力赛。太完美了！
It's actually raining, I'm in a rally.This is perfect!

1123
01:05:36,560 --> 01:05:38,119
（哈蒙德大笑）
(HAMMOND LAUGHING)

1124
01:05:41,440 --> 01:05:44,239
在尝了那么多愚蠢的食物，看了那么多破砖烂瓦后
After all the stupid food and looking at rocks,

1125
01:05:45,040 --> 01:05:49,199
我终于干了一件让我兴奋异常的事...
to come out and do something genuinely exciting and real and...

1126
01:05:49,880 --> 01:05:51,519
我又充满了激情
I've come alive.

1127
01:05:53,800 --> 01:05:54,799
哦，太棒了！
Oh, yes!

1128
01:05:55,400 --> 01:05:57,079
（雷神大作）
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

1129
01:05:57,960 --> 01:06:00,719
哈蒙德正在这样的大雨里在外面抽风
Hammond is out now in that.

1130
01:06:04,520 --> 01:06:06,319
他简直疯了！
The man is insane!

1131
01:06:11,120 --> 01:06:13,839
来吧，再下大点。来啊！
Bring it on, let's have more. Come on!

1132
01:06:14,600 --> 01:06:15,599
这也叫下雨？
You call that rain?

1133
01:06:16,600 --> 01:06:18,039
（大笑）
(LAUGHING)

1134
01:06:19,920 --> 01:06:21,439
（大笑）喔！
(LAUGHING) Oh!

1135
01:06:21,520 --> 01:06:24,519
现在这里是这个世界上我最喜欢的地方
This is my favourite place in the world now.

1136
01:06:26,520 --> 01:06:27,519
（雷雨交加）
(THUNDER CRACKING)

1137
01:06:27,640 --> 01:06:28,639
哈蒙德：啊哈！
HAMMOND: Ah!

1138
01:06:28,720 --> 01:06:30,919
抱歉，哈蒙德，给我解释解释
I'm sorry, Hammond,do try to explain it to me,

1139
01:06:31,000 --> 01:06:33,079
我实在难以理解
'cause I'm struggling to get it.

1140
01:06:33,160 --> 01:06:35,799
这是本次旅程中我干过最爽的事情了
It's about the most fun I've had in a very long time.

1141
01:06:35,880 --> 01:06:37,439
我能理解为什么Stig经常来这了
I can see why The Stig comes here.

1142
01:06:37,760 --> 01:06:39,399
-你全身是泥。-是的
-You're covered in mud. -Yeah.

1143
01:06:39,480 --> 01:06:41,959
-外面雷雨交加。-是的，我知道
-There's a massive thunderstorm raging. -Yeah, I know.

1144
01:06:42,040 --> 01:06:43,999
我明白，没有比这更好的天气了。太完美了
I know, even the weather's better here.It's perfect.

1145
01:06:44,080 --> 01:06:45,199
你说更好是什么意思？
What do you mean, it's better?

1146
01:06:45,560 --> 01:06:46,999
（雷声）
(THUNDER RUMBLES)

1147
01:06:48,360 --> 01:06:49,359
（开门声）
(CAR BEEPING)

1148
01:06:49,480 --> 01:06:51,239
-哈蒙德，我一定要这么干吗？-是的
-Hammond, do I have to do this? -Yep.

1149
01:06:51,360 --> 01:06:54,399
（叹气）今天我做主，这就是我们今天的任务
(SIGHS) It's my thing today,and this is what we're doing.

1150
01:06:54,760 --> 01:06:57,519
克拉克森：就这样，为了表现出我是个多么大度的人
CLARKSON: Andso, to show what a good sport I am,

1151
01:06:57,960 --> 01:06:59,319
我逼着自己出发了
I obliged.

1152
01:07:01,760 --> 01:07:03,759
噢，上帝啊！
Oh, God's truth!

1153
01:07:07,000 --> 01:07:08,639
噢！真疼
Oh! That hurt.

1154
01:07:09,840 --> 01:07:10,999
真难受...
So, discomfort...

1155
01:07:12,360 --> 01:07:14,799
噢！真是太恶心了！
Oh! That's just horrible!

1156
01:07:16,080 --> 01:07:17,079
危险
Danger.

1157
01:07:17,520 --> 01:07:19,399
悲惨，湿冷
Misery, cold.

1158
01:07:22,160 --> 01:07:24,879
打滑让我只能开到21英里的时速（34公里）
Slithering around at 21 miles an hour.

1159
01:07:25,480 --> 01:07:27,239
哦，不！见鬼...
Oh, no! Bloody...

1160
01:07:28,560 --> 01:07:30,599
我洗了个泥水澡
I've just had a brown shower.

1161
01:07:31,800 --> 01:07:34,519
原本以为这一圈就结束了
That really was the final straw.

1162
01:07:34,800 --> 01:07:35,799
（雷声）
(THUNDER RUMBLES)

1163
01:07:36,080 --> 01:07:38,639
后来才发现噩梦远没结束
And then it turned out it wasn't.

1164
01:07:39,320 --> 01:07:42,639
好的，刚才是热身圈，我们已经熟悉了赛道，对吧？
So, we got the hang of it,we now know the course, yeah?

1165
01:07:43,160 --> 01:07:44,919
现在开始跑计时赛
Time for timed laps.

1166
01:07:45,800 --> 01:07:47,039
-什么？-是的，现在开始跑计时赛
-What? -Well, we do timed laps now,

1167
01:07:47,120 --> 01:07:49,439
这才是正题。我觉得我们每人再跑上十圈
that's what we do.I reckon if we do 1 0 each

1168
01:07:49,520 --> 01:07:51,639
就能得出谁是最优秀的车手
and then we can just work out how consistent we are,

1169
01:07:51,720 --> 01:07:54,319
在成绩上一见高低，怎么样？
where we can just shave those extra seconds out, yeah?

1170
01:07:54,720 --> 01:07:56,919
明天，我会请你吃
Tomorrow, you are going to eat

1171
01:07:57,000 --> 01:07:59,159
野熊的蛋蛋
a badger's left teste.

1172
01:08:02,480 --> 01:08:05,839
克拉克森：结果，我们全然不顾外面的瓢泼大雨
CLARKSON: Andso, flying in the face of common sense,

1173
01:08:07,440 --> 01:08:08,719
又回到了赛道上
we got back out there.

1174
01:08:13,240 --> 01:08:16,279
计时赛，所以这回是动真格的
Timed laps now, so it's really critical

1175
01:08:16,360 --> 01:08:19,239
要勇敢地踩下油门
to just be brave enough to keep that power in.

1176
01:08:20,480 --> 01:08:22,439
（哈蒙德大笑）
(HAMMOND LAUGHING)

1177
01:08:22,720 --> 01:08:24,959
克拉克森：计时赛有什么意义？
CLARKSON: What's the point of timed laps?

1178
01:08:25,600 --> 01:08:29,039
他比我多80马力...噢！...比我多得多
He's got 80 more horsepower...Oh! ...more than I have.

1179
01:08:29,480 --> 01:08:31,359
他比我更擅长玩这个
He's better at it than I am.

1180
01:08:31,480 --> 01:08:34,119
他配置了限滑差速器
And he's got a limited-slip differential.

1181
01:08:35,320 --> 01:08:36,519
我什么都没有
I haven't got one of those.

1182
01:08:36,600 --> 01:08:40,279
所以每当我过弯，我的一个轮子就会打滑
So, when I go round the corner,one wheel spins and that's it.

1183
01:08:43,280 --> 01:08:46,759
哦嚯！天啊，当你做出完美滑行的时候那感觉太爽了
Woo-hoo! God, it feels good when you get it right.

1184
01:08:49,400 --> 01:08:50,399
哇噢！
Whoa!

1185
01:08:50,920 --> 01:08:52,399
噢!哦，我的天！
Oh! Oh, my!

1186
01:08:52,720 --> 01:08:54,279
（大笑）
(LAUGHING)

1187
01:08:55,160 --> 01:08:56,159
他也会...
He will have been...

1188
01:08:58,840 --> 01:09:01,359
噢，看见他了，我能从这里看见他的大白牙
Oh, here he comes,I can see his teeth from here.

1189
01:09:03,560 --> 01:09:07,079
好的，拉力赛的弯道超车。真有意思
Right, overtaking on a rally stage.This is interesting.

1190
01:09:10,320 --> 01:09:11,319
克拉克森：噢，他超过了我！
CLARKSON: Oh, he's coming through!

1191
01:09:11,840 --> 01:09:15,119
噢，不！丑陋的伯明翰小矮子超过了我！
Oh, no! The hideous little Brummie has torn past!

1192
01:09:15,400 --> 01:09:17,319
啊哈！追上你了！
A-ha! Got you!

1193
01:09:18,800 --> 01:09:20,839
噢，他居然这么干...噢，他全都做到了
Oh, he's done it...Oh, he's just made everything

1194
01:09:20,920 --> 01:09:23,439
更糟的是，我看不见任何东西
much worse now, I can't see a thing.

1195
01:09:26,800 --> 01:09:27,799
一片模糊
Muddy goggles.

1196
01:09:29,840 --> 01:09:30,839
（呻吟）
(GROANS)

1197
01:09:33,600 --> 01:09:38,159
我真想把他弄成残废
Every bone in his crotch,that is what I'm going to break.

1198
01:09:41,760 --> 01:09:43,119
（大笑）
(LAUGHING)

1199
01:09:44,480 --> 01:09:45,479
喔！
Oh!

1200
01:09:47,720 --> 01:09:49,519
克拉克森：很快，天气变得越来越糟
CLARKSON: Soon, the weather got so bad,

1201
01:09:49,600 --> 01:09:51,999
甚至哈蒙德也看不清赛道了
even Hammond couldn't see where he was going.

1202
01:09:53,520 --> 01:09:56,159
见鬼！见鬼！噢！
Shit! Shit! Oh!

1203
01:09:57,840 --> 01:10:02,239
克拉克森：因此，他提议先暂停，享用一顿拉力午餐
CLARKSON: So, he suggested we stop for one of his special rallying lunches.

1204
01:10:03,680 --> 01:10:05,559
唔。尽情享用
Mmm. Okay, tuck in.

1205
01:10:05,960 --> 01:10:07,839
-真的？-唔-唔
-Really? -Mmm-hmm.

1206
01:10:07,920 --> 01:10:10,999
这是法国本地的特色热狗
'Cause this part of France is famous for its hotdogs.

1207
01:10:11,280 --> 01:10:12,959
这上面抹了法式芥末酱
It's got French mustard on it.

1208
01:10:13,520 --> 01:10:15,519
-是的...-等等
-Yeah... -Wait a minute.

1209
01:10:15,600 --> 01:10:16,599
什么？
What?

1210
01:10:16,880 --> 01:10:18,799
你知道这热狗肠里都是些什么吗？
You do know what's in that sausage, don't you?

1211
01:10:19,360 --> 01:10:21,519
-香肠。-猪蹄子
-Sausage. -Pigs' toenails,

1212
01:10:21,600 --> 01:10:22,599
猪的睫毛...
eyelashes...

1213
01:10:24,280 --> 01:10:28,159
闭嘴快吃。趁你享用美食的时候，我手里已经有咱俩的成绩了
Shut up and enjoy it. And, anyway, while you enjoy it, 
I've got the timings here.

1214
01:10:28,400 --> 01:10:31,959
我在1分16秒，13秒之间
I'm around the 1:16, 1:13,that kind of mark.

1215
01:10:32,040 --> 01:10:34,799
-唔-唔。-你的成绩在1分53，46...
-Mmm-hmm. -You're 1:53,1:46...

1216
01:10:34,880 --> 01:10:36,679
克拉克森：泥巴都进到我的耳朵里了！
CLARKSON: I've got soil in my ears!

1217
01:10:36,760 --> 01:10:40,919
1分35，1分40...基本上，可以看出
1：35,1：40... Basically, what this is showing is that I am clearly

1218
01:10:41,000 --> 01:10:42,999
我比你快得多
a lot better at this than you.

1219
01:10:43,080 --> 01:10:44,439
-我要和你再打个赌。-什么？
-I'll do you a deal. -What?

1220
01:10:44,520 --> 01:10:46,359
我们再跑一圈。
We will do one more lap.

1221
01:10:46,440 --> 01:10:47,559
生死战
Do-or-die lap.

1222
01:10:48,440 --> 01:10:52,119
如果我赢了，我立马消失
If I'm faster, we leave immediately.

1223
01:10:52,200 --> 01:10:53,399
-如果你比我快？-是的
-If you're faster than me? -Yes.

1224
