01:21:21,480 --> 01:21:24,999
我们又重温了一遍本次旅行用到的各种
we ruminated on all the boats and bikes and cars

1380
01:21:25,280 --> 01:21:27,519
游艇，摩托车，跑车
that we'd used on ourjourney.

1381
01:21:30,320 --> 01:21:32,199
-哈蒙德！-（笑）
-Hammond! -(LAUGHING)

1382
01:21:33,040 --> 01:21:37,359
我们也试图找出一款最优秀的交通工具
And we tried to work out which one we'd liked the best.

1383
01:21:38,600 --> 01:21:39,879
（尖叫）
(SCREAMING)

1384
01:21:43,960 --> 01:21:47,079
我喜欢那辆福特嘉年华ST，我真的很喜欢
I loved that little Fiesta ST,I really did.

1385
01:21:47,440 --> 01:21:50,519
我喜欢驾驶那辆福特T型车，虽然它开起来很疯狂
I actually loved driving the Model-T,crazy though that is.

1386
01:21:50,920 --> 01:21:52,759
我喜欢那辆杜卡迪
I enjoyed the Ducati.

1387
01:21:52,920 --> 01:21:57,119
但出于某些原因，法拉利F12给我留下了很深的印象
But for some reason, the Ferrari F12 has really stayed with me.

1388
01:21:57,200 --> 01:22:00,639
我认为它既高贵又漂亮而且还很快！
I thought it had presence and drama and it's fast!

1389
01:22:00,800 --> 01:22:05,479
我不会选SLS因为它体积太大，不适合日常使用
I wouldn't have the SLS 'cause that's too much to use every day.

1390
01:22:06,960 --> 01:22:09,359
高尔夫GTI又太小了
Golf GTI isn't quite enough.

1391
01:22:10,440 --> 01:22:13,079
布加迪威龙，我是说它又是另一个级别的产物了
Bugatti Veyron, I mean it's the other end of the scale, then.

1392
01:22:14,000 --> 01:22:15,879
高出太多。宾利...
Too much. Bentley...

1393
01:22:16,760 --> 01:22:20,159
噢，是辆不错的车但是...我想出来了我喜欢什么
Oh, it's a great car but...I've worked out what I'd have.

1394
01:22:22,200 --> 01:22:24,679
丽娃Aquarama（那艘豪华游艇- -#）
The Riva Aquarama. (LAUGHING)

1395
01:22:25,000 --> 01:22:26,279
-那是你最喜欢的车？-是的
-That's your favourite car? -Yes.

1396
01:22:26,360 --> 01:22:29,279
如果我天天用它，我估计得搬家
That's what I'd use every day.I'd have to move house.

1397
01:22:32,080 --> 01:22:35,159
得出结论之后，我们爬进各自的爱车
With that decided,we climbed back into our road cars

1398
01:22:35,240 --> 01:22:37,479
前往最后的目的地波城
for the final push to Pau.

1399
01:22:40,520 --> 01:22:43,079
我们对前方的圣城是如此兴奋
We were very excited by what lay ahead,

1400
01:22:43,160 --> 01:22:46,639
以至于我们不顾摄制组的后勤车一骑绝尘
so excited that we left the camera crew far behind.

1401
01:22:47,360 --> 01:22:50,959
当他们再次赶上我们的时候，我们遇到了一点小麻烦
And when they finally caught up with us,there was a bit of a problem.

1402
01:22:52,760 --> 01:22:55,479
（警察无线电通讯，模糊不清）
(POLICE RADIO CHATTER, INDISTINCT)

1403
01:22:56,640 --> 01:22:57,799
克拉克森：你是说，护照？
CLARKSON: You mean, passports?

1404
01:22:58,160 --> 01:23:00,759
噢，好吧
Oh, right.

1405
01:23:01,880 --> 01:23:04,279
那边的法国男警官和女警官
The French policemen and lady policemen

1406
01:23:04,480 --> 01:23:07,839
坚持让我们交出随身携带的所有的现金（难道遇上劫道的了...）
insisted that we should give them all our money.

1407
01:23:07,840 --> 01:23:09,919
最后经过漫长的交涉
And then after quite a long chat,

1408
01:23:10,080 --> 01:23:14,239
他们决定如果我们不在法国驾车就允许我们入境
they decided it would be best if we didn't drive in France any more.

1409
01:23:14,560 --> 01:23:15,799
好吧，就这样
Yeah, okay.

1410
01:23:24,720 --> 01:23:28,199
随着这则爆炸性消息，又到了节目结束的时候
And on that bombshell,it is time to end.

1411
01:23:28,280 --> 01:23:30,479
非常感谢各位的观看，再见
Thank you very much for watching,goodbye.

1412
01:23:31,120 --> 01:23:33,119
你这个白痴！
You total plonker!

1413
01:23:42,120 --> 01:23:45,719
我不想搭标致或者波罗
I don't want to go in a Peugeot or a Polo.

1414
01:23:53,760 --> 01:23:55,999
或是这辆沃克斯豪尔赛飞利
Or this Vauxhall Zafira.

1415
01:23:56,000 --> 01:23:57,989
搭顺风车的人能这么挑剔吗？
Can you be picky when you're a hitchhiker?

1416
01:23:57,990 --> 01:23:60,789
我觉得可以。这有太多车可以选择了
I should think so.There's plenty of choice.

1417
01:24:11,400 --> 01:24:13,039
不想上那辆雪铁龙
Don't want to go in that Citroen.

